on": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "assignees": [{"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2018-04-04T15:35:43Z", "updated_at": "2018-04-05T22:28:08Z", "closed_at": "2018-04-05T22:28:08Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "An inner doc comment `//! doc` currently incorrectly tokenizes as an outer attribute, `#[doc = \"//! doc\"]`. It should be an inner attribute, `#![doc = \" doc\"]`. You can see the correct behavior in macro_rules:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nmacro_rules! tokens {\r\n    (#![doc = $tt:tt]) => {\r\n        println!(\"{:?}\", $tt);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    tokens! {\r\n        //! doc\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Repro script\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n#!/bin/sh\r\n\r\ncargo new --lib repro_macro\r\ncargo new --lib repro\r\n\r\necho >repro_macro/src/lib.rs '\r\n#![feature(proc_macro)]\r\n\r\nextern crate proc_macro;\r\nuse proc_macro::TokenStream;\r\n\r\n#[proc_macro]\r\npub fn repro(_input: TokenStream) -> TokenStream {\r\n    let mut tts = \"//! doc\\n\".parse::<TokenStream>().unwrap().into_iter();\r\n    println!(\"{}\", tts.next().unwrap());\r\n    println!(\"{}\", tts.next().unwrap());\r\n    TokenStream::empty()\r\n}\r\n'\r\n\r\necho >>repro_macro/Cargo.toml '\r\n[lib]\r\nproc-macro = true\r\n'\r\n\r\necho >repro/src/lib.rs '\r\n#![feature(proc_macro)]\r\n\r\nextern crate repro_macro;\r\nrepro_macro::repro!();\r\n'\r\n\r\necho >>repro/Cargo.toml '\r\nrepro_macro = { path = \"../repro_macro\" }\r\n'\r\n\r\ncargo build --manifest-path repro/Cargo.toml\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n#\r\n[ doc = \"//! doc\" ]\r\n```\r\n\r\n@alexcrichton ", "closed_by": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.g